2a:["$","p","p-17",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"Spot long + short perp to collect funding. Similar to what Ethena does. Works when funding is positive."}]
2b:["$","p","p-18",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"className":"text-foreground font-semibold","children":"Catch:"}]," In bear markets, funding frequently goes negative (shorts pay longs, not the other way). Single-exchange basis trading can lose money in sustained bear markets. This is why Ethena maintains a ",["$","a","a-0",{"href":"https://docs.ethena.fi/solution-overview/risks/funding-risk","className":"text-primary underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-primary/80 transition-colors","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer","children":"reserve fund"}]," — to absorb negative funding periods."]}]
