2e:["$","p","p-20",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"Single-exchange basis trading (spot + short perp on Binance) works when funding rates are positive. When the market turns bearish and funding goes negative, you're paying to hold the position instead of getting paid."}]
